{"tid":1509444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極重要］2019香港革命網demo出現了！！","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:20:46.000Z","uid":232014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52b8d35b91308dc4d7b61deb8942fd7b02a6268c","tid":1509444,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼上個禮拜初次招兵：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 2019香港革命網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486248</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家想同大家講有手足已經幫我地做左個網站demo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/88brw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F88brw&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=6da5b5bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/88brw</a><br />\n<br />\n而家終於有機會比因為各種上唔到前線既手足可以係呢個運動上出一分力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家可以盡你地既能力搵返哂有關呢一次運動既資料出黎！</span>用黎比返抗爭動力我地又好，第時用黎做教材又好，希望可以將所有事做個記錄！搵到既資料請用google form形式比我地：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScNMRYsuOfZ4pKWbrlSlHQWWHJpgcM5zug8B_pGrE7Fn-SbWA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScNMRYsuOfZ4pKWbrlSlHQWWHJpgcM5zug8B_pGrE7Fn-SbWA%2Fviewform&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=ca9a36ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScNMRYsuOfZ4pKWbrlSlHQWWHJpgcM5zug8B_pGrE7Fn-SbWA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n另外亦都想擴展團隊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足有興趣幫手整合資料或比IT意見，可以tg pm:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/savehknochinazi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsavehknochinazi&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=2d443768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/savehknochinazi</a><br />\n<br />\n如果呢方面想討論，亦可以入公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/letsnotforgethk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fletsnotforgethk&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=19fccc59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/letsnotforgethk</a><br />\n<br />\n求下咁多位冇野做既話，可唔可以都幫幫手搵啲資料返黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一條已經好多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！唔好白費手足辛辛苦苦整出黎既demo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247dbcb5ff78138702b3f233c889888b9b1727fe","tid":1509444,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=f0e18421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=99e1d18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=6ee13c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a